VARDESC: Was the child allowed put the mouthpiece into his/her mouth and blow with the nose clip on the nose?
Was the child provided a demonstration and encouraged to inspire fully into the spirometer and blow fast?
Which position is the child in during this test?
Was the manuever successful? The child should have at least two to three successful and reproducible manuevers
What is the Forced Vital Capacity (FVC)?
What is the Forced Expiratory Volume in .5 seconds (FEV.5)?
What is the Forced Expiratory Volume in .75 seconds (FEV.75)?
What is the Forced Expiratory Volume in 1 second (FEV1)?
What is the repeatability of parameters above?
What is the number of satisfactory attempts (maneuvers)?
